skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my workout
des:
Welcome to My Workout, or rather, YOUR Workout!

Discover a new way to train, combining your personal preferences, Artificial Intelligence, and Alexa!

Visit our portal at https://myworkoutskill.com and create your workouts manually or with the incredible power of our Artificial Intelligence.

Don't know how to create a workout? No problem!

At https://myworkoutskill.com, you can choose the muscle groups you want to train, the available equipment you have at home, the intensity of the workouts, and the rest is on us! In a matter of seconds, your complete workout will be ready and synced with your Alexa.

# List of available actions:

"Alexa, begin My Workout"
"Alexa, (rest/pause/break/interval) in My Workout"
"Alexa, ask My Workout to finish"
"Alexa, ask My Workout to resume"
